<p>The program will remain on the site indefinitely. OIG Outlook 2014 is not copyrighted; however, OIG does not have the resources to produce or distribute DVDs of this program. Because of your organization's unique security requirements and software capabilities OIG cannot recommend the best way to access and download the videos. Please contact your IT department to help access and download the videos from YouTube. </p>



